&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-01-06 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-7860/log-29974/"&gt;Doing Useful Work&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
